---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Visual First on Mobile, Second on Desktop -->
        <div class="fade-in order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Main Card -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl text-white">
              <Icon name="lucide:code" class="w-16 h-16 mb-6 opacity-90" />
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Hour of Code</h3>
              <p class="text-green-50 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                從 2013 年開始，吸引超過 180 個國家、數億名學生參與的全球性程式教育運動
              </p>

              <!-- Decorative Elements -->
              <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
              <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Floating Cards -->
            <div class="absolute -right-8 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 hidden lg:block">
              <Icon name="lucide:clock" class="w-8 h-8 text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2" />
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">1 小時</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">快速入門</div>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute -left-8 bottom-8 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 hidden lg:block">
              <Icon name="lucide:globe" class="w-8 h-8 text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2" />
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">全球</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">教育運動</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="fade-in order-1 md:order-2">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-green-50 rounded-full mb-6">
            <Icon name="lucide:info" class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-primary)]" />
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)]">Code.org 發起</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            關於 Hour of Code
          </h2>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            「Hour of Code」由 <strong>Code.org</strong> 發起，是一項全球性的教育運動。自 2013 年開始，短短幾年間已經吸引超過 180 個國家、數億名學生參與。
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            活動設計以<strong class="text-[var(--color-primary)]">一小時的程式體驗</strong>為核心，降低入門門檻，讓所有人都能嘗試寫程式。
          </p>

          <!-- Key Features -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-xl border border-green-100">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">零門檻入門</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">不需要任何程式基礎，就能開始學習</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-xl border border-green-100">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">趣味學習</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">透過遊戲化的方式，讓學習充滿樂趣</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-xl border border-green-100">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">全年齡適用</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">從 4 歲到 104 歲，人人都能參與</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
  }
</style>
